<td><div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="description en" style="display:inline;"><i>This logo image consists only of simple geometric shapes or text. It <b>does not meet the <a href="/wiki/Commons:Threshold_of_originality" title="Commons:Threshold of originality">threshold of originality</a></b> needed for copyright protection, and is therefore in the <b><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/public_domain" class="extiw" title="w:public domain">public domain</a></b>. Although it is free of copyright restrictions, this image may still be subject to <a href="/wiki/Commons:Non-copyright_restrictions" title="Commons:Non-copyright restrictions">other restrictions</a>. See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Public_domain#Fonts_and_typefaces" class="extiw" title="w:Wikipedia:Public domain">WP:PD §&#160;Fonts and typefaces</a> or <a href="/wiki/Template_talk:PD-textlogo" title="Template talk:PD-textlogo">Template talk:PD-textlogo</a> for more information.</i></div>
